Sentece: A high value of urinary excretion (mean 76.9% of infused dose) and a mean clearance of 8.42 L/h were found, suggesting the presence of tubular secretion.
Title: Pharmacokinetic analysis of azelaic acid disodium salt. A proposed substrate for total parenteral nutrition.
Name: Azelaic Acid
